    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "resistance? idk man. it just feels kinda delusional to call it that. like, if you knew a building was definitely going to fall on you, you wouldn't call \"staying in the room\" an act of resistance. you'd just get out. i feel like people are just terrified to admit that there's really no way out of this and that just letting go is the only honest thing left to do.",
